    <item>
      <title>以色列准备应对伊朗袭击，油价升至十月高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/oil-shoots-to-6-month-high-as-middle-east-conflict-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列准备应对伊朗可能发动的袭击，石油价格跃升至十月份以来的最高水平，这一事态发展将威胁到占世界原油产量三分之一的地区的重大破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/oil-shoots-to-6-month-high-as-middle-east-conflict-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 13:41:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度通胀在民意调查前降至10个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/india-inflation-cools-in-march-on-decline-in-food-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于食品和燃料价格下跌，印度 3 月份零售通胀降至 10 个月低点，尽管即将到来的热浪可能会损害农作物并有可能推高价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/india-inflation-cools-in-march-on-decline-in-food-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴货币因规避风险而跌至三个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/emerging-market-currencies-hit-two-month-low-on-flight-from-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币跌至近三个月来的最低水平，股市抹去了本周的涨幅，原因是美国利率前景发生转变，地缘政治紧张局势加剧引发了避险情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/emerging-market-currencies-hit-two-month-low-on-flight-from-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:42:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>矿石短缺满足需求复苏，铜价持续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lme-copper-rises-to-highest-since-june-2022-as-outlook-brightens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价继续上涨，触及 2022 年 6 月以来的最高水平，因为投资者押注减少的矿石供应将难以跟上全球不断增长的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lme-copper-rises-to-highest-since-june-2022-as-outlook-brightens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:14:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元的五个月低点加剧了欧洲央行与美联储分歧的平价讨论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/euro-falls-to-five-month-low-as-ecb-fed-divergence-looms-large</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧洲央行似乎将在美联储之前降息，欧元跌至今年的最低水平，引发了市场对欧元可能进一步下跌多少的讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/euro-falls-to-five-month-low-as-ecb-fed-divergence-looms-large</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:23:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国表示汽车贷款公司应为调查造成的财务影响做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/uk-says-car-loan-firms-should-prep-for-probe-s-financial-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融行为监管局警告汽车金融公司开始为汽车金融产品审查可能产生的额外成本做好准备，因为近几个月来，贷款机构在是否立即对盈利造成影响方面存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/uk-says-car-loan-firms-should-prep-for-probe-s-financial-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 06:55:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
